---
import { empathyStats } from "../../data/prototype";
import WorldMap from "./WorldMap.astro";
---

<section class="prototype-section empathy-scene" id="empathy" data-prototype-section data-title="停电时刻">
  <div class="scene-map scene-map--empathy">
    <WorldMap className="world-map-svg" landClass="world-map-land world-map-land--empathy" />
  </div>

  <div class="empathy-blackout" data-empathy-blackout></div>

  <div class="empathy-copy" data-empathy-copy>
    <p class="section-kicker reveal" style="--delay: 0.1s">停电不是抽象概念</p>
    <h2 class="empathy-title reveal" style="--delay: 0.22s">它会让城市失去节奏，让时间忽然变重。</h2>
    <p class="empathy-subtitle reveal" style="--delay: 0.34s">
      当照明、通信、交通和供暖一起退出，电网脆弱性就不再只是课本里的术语。
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="empathy-dark-text" data-empathy-dark-text>
    <p>这就是大停电真正让人记住的部分。</p>
    <p>不是数字，而是突然到来的黑暗。</p>
  </div>

  <div class="stats-row" data-empathy-stats>
    {empathyStats.map((stat) => (
      <div class="stat-item">
        <span class="stat-label">{stat.label}</span>
        <strong class="stat-number">{stat.value}</strong>
        <span class="stat-unit">{stat.unit}</span>
      </div>
    ))}
  </div>
</section>
